<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 18:08:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加沙战争爆发一个月后，以色列正在经历一个超越政治的时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/one-month-into-gaza-war-israel-is-experiencing-a-moment-that-transcends-politics/0000018b-afbe-d3c1-a39b-bfff853a0000</link><description>极端正统派男子正在为军队签名，阿拉伯以色列人正在与犹太以色列人一起帮助流离失所者。但不要过于乐观——自 10 月 7 日以来，本杰明·内塔尼亚胡和他的顽固支持者并没有改变</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 17:45:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/one-month-into-gaza-war-israel-is-experiencing-a-moment-that-transcends-politics/0000018b-afbe-d3c1-a39b-bfff853a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府将接受私人捐款资助加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-government-will-accept-private-donations-to-fund-war-in-gaza/0000018b-af50-dea2-a9bf-ffde12340000</link><description>批评者表示，该指令为外部对政府优先事项的不当影响和对普通公民的剥削打开了大门</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 16:57:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/economy-finance/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-government-will-accept-private-donations-to-fund-war-in-gaza/0000018b-af50-dea2-a9bf-ffde12340000</guid></item><item><title>以色列扣留资金帮助战争撤离人员的真正原因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/the-real-reason-israel-is-holding-up-money-to-help-war-evacuees/0000018b-af8d-df42-a78f-afcfabe10000</link><description>没有钱请正统派老师吗？那么以色列战争撤离者也没有钱：以色列政府试图淡化这个等式</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 16:25:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/the-real-reason-israel-is-holding-up-money-to-help-war-evacuees/0000018b-af8d-df42-a78f-afcfabe10000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔的认罪笔录在他发动的战争中重新审视</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leader-yahya-sinwars-confession-transcript-reexamined-amid-a-war-he-started/0000018b-af64-dea2-a9bf-fffe1c080000</link><description>随着以色列在加沙对哈马斯发动战争，有关哈马斯领导人和 10 月 7 日建筑师叶海亚·辛瓦尔 (Yahya Sinwar) 的记忆被重新唤起，他曾因谋杀罪在以色列服无期徒刑。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 16:20:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/hamas-leader-yahya-sinwars-confession-transcript-reexamined-amid-a-war-he-started/0000018b-af64-dea2-a9bf-fffe1c080000</guid></item><item><title>“即使在伦敦也很可怕”：六名以色列人逃离该国开始新生活</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/even-here-in-london-its-scary-what-being-an-israeli-abroad-now-is-like/0000018b-ae87-df42-a78f-afc7cf810000</link><description>奥里特（Orit）是一位导乐师，虽然身在佐治亚州，但仍在帮助她的老客户生孩子；安德烈（Andrey）对他所看到的视频感到震惊；亚登（Yarden）正在勇敢地面对伦敦喧闹的抗议活动</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 15:48:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/even-here-in-london-its-scary-what-being-an-israeli-abroad-now-is-like/0000018b-ae87-df42-a78f-afc7cf810000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列的内塔尼亚胡仍然向普京和俄罗斯卑躬屈膝？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-is-israels-netanyahu-still-groveling-to-putin-and-russia/0000018b-af21-dea2-a9bf-ffbf3e0c0000</link><description>十年来，以色列一直急于安抚莫斯科。但内塔尼亚胡坦率地对莫斯科采取令人尴尬的绥靖政策并没有带来明显的收获。相反，在 10 月 7 日的暴行发生后，普京立即加强了与伊朗的合作并接待了哈马斯领导人</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 15:20:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-is-israels-netanyahu-still-groveling-to-putin-and-russia/0000018b-af21-dea2-a9bf-ffbf3e0c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列模特被选为迪奥广告大片后，亲巴勒斯坦活动人士呼吁抵制</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/pro-palestinian-activists-call-for-boycott-after-israeli-model-is-chosen-for-dior-campaign/0000018b-af36-dea2-a9bf-ffbe3be30000</link><description>这家著名的法国时装公司邀请以色列人 May Tager 参与圣诞广告活动，引发了社交媒体上大量愤怒的帖子。 “迪奥选择凶手是为了他们的竞选活动，现在一切都散发着血腥味”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 15:01:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/pro-palestinian-activists-call-for-boycott-after-israeli-model-is-chosen-for-dior-campaign/0000018b-af36-dea2-a9bf-ffbe3be30000</guid></item><item><title>共和党总统候选人在迈阿密辩论中激烈交锋，巴勒斯坦人、反犹太主义成为首要议程</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-top-hit-list-as-gop-candidates-minus-trump-lock-horns-in-miami-debate/0000018b-af10-d3c1-a39b-bff18cde0000</link><description>尽管前总统唐纳德·特朗普缺席了周三由共和党犹太联盟共同发起的电视辩论，但随着候选人讨论以色列-加沙战争和国内反犹太主义抬头，他的影响力将不容忽视</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 14:50:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/palestinians-top-hit-list-as-gop-candidates-minus-trump-lock-horns-in-miami-debate/0000018b-af10-d3c1-a39b-bff18cde0000</guid></item><item><title>埃及就以色列-加沙停火、释放哈马斯扣押的部分人质举行高级会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-live/soldier-killed-in-gaza-biden-confirms-asking-netanyahu-for-humanitarian-pause/0000018b-ad28-d0f8-a39b-fd3a1c820000</link><description>以色列国防军公布了在加沙战斗中丧生的两名士兵的姓名 ■ 布林肯首先明确呼吁巴勒斯坦领导的治理，并在巴勒斯坦权力机构的支持下加沙与西岸统一 ■ 加兰特表示，以色列将在战后在加沙拥有充分的行动自由 ■由于需要资助战争，以色列总检察长下令冻结联军资金 ■ 10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀中至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵死亡，241 名人质在加沙被扣，40 人下落不明 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：超过 10,000 人被杀</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 14:01:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-live/soldier-killed-in-gaza-biden-confirms-asking-netanyahu-for-humanitarian-pause/0000018b-ad28-d0f8-a39b-fd3a1c820000</guid></item><item><title>以色列厨师埃亚尔·沙尼 (Eyal Shani) 在为以色列国防军士兵煎牛排时荣获首颗米其林星</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/while-flipping-steaks-for-idf-soldiers-israeli-chef-eyal-shani-gets-first-michelin-star/0000018b-af1e-d3c1-a39b-bfff8fdc0000</link><description>这位著名的以色列餐厅老板以其纽约餐厅“Shmona”赢得了顶级烹饪皇冠上的宝石。沙尼 (Shani) 成为第四位获得米其林星的以色列厨师</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 13:57:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/while-flipping-steaks-for-idf-soldiers-israeli-chef-eyal-shani-gets-first-michelin-star/0000018b-af1e-d3c1-a39b-bfff8fdc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的战争，冲突已持续一个月。什么样的未来？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-with-hamas-one-month-into-the-conflict-what-lies-ahead/0000018b-aeaa-d3c1-a39b-beeb5d510000</link><description>《国土报》和加州大学洛杉矶分校举办了一场视频讨论，讨论以色列潜在的退出战略、政治后果和公众在加沙战争中的沮丧情绪：“我们正走向政治动荡最激烈的时期之一”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 13:24:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-war-with-hamas-one-month-into-the-conflict-what-lies-ahead/0000018b-aeaa-d3c1-a39b-beeb5d510000</guid></item><item><title>考古学家可能在加利利海发现了耶稣使徒的传统家园</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/archaeologists-find-site-early-christians-venerated-as-apostle-peters-home/0000018b-ae8c-d3c1-a39b-beedd7520000</link><description>在他们认为是伯赛大的村庄里一座早期教堂的下面，考古学家发现了一堵“圣墙”——这不可能是来自使徒彼得的房子。然而，旁边的那个可能是</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 13:09:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/archaeologists-find-site-early-christians-venerated-as-apostle-peters-home/0000018b-ae8c-d3c1-a39b-beedd7520000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗核事务负责人：部长威胁“用核武器攻击加沙”证实了以色列的能力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/iran-nuclear-chief-ministers-threat-to-nuke-gaza-confirms-israels-capability/0000018b-aecb-df42-a78f-afcbcbcd0000</link><description>伊朗的穆罕默德·伊斯拉米表示，“犹太复国主义政权已经承认拥有核武器，更重要的是，威胁着加沙受压迫的无辜人民”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 12:35:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/iran-nuclear-chief-ministers-threat-to-nuke-gaza-confirms-israels-capability/0000018b-aecb-df42-a78f-afcbcbcd0000</guid></item><item><title>针头和造成的伤害：为什么以色列人用纹身来纪念 10 月 7 日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-needle-and-the-damage-done-why-israelis-are-marking-october-7-with-tattoos/0000018b-aa73-d738-a5eb-fbf347be0000</link><description>以色列的纹身店从未如此繁忙，以色列人希望纪念哈马斯大屠杀。特拉维夫的一位艺术家表示，他正在告诉那些被痛苦和愤怒所吞噬的潜在客户考虑他们是否真的想要纹身来永久提醒他们恐怖</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 11:12:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-needle-and-the-damage-done-why-israelis-are-marking-october-7-with-tattoos/0000018b-aa73-d738-a5eb-fbf347be0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登要求内塔尼亚胡暂停人道主义援助，讨论后哈马斯加沙的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/biden-asks-netanyahu-for-humanitarian-pauses-discusses-plans-for-a-post-hamas-gaza/0000018b-ae50-df42-a78f-af53709f0000</link><description>美国和以色列继续就停火、人质和战后计划进行对话，维持反对加沙全面停火的坚定立场；布林肯表示哈马斯将尝试重复“10月7日，一次又一次”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 10:20:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/biden-asks-netanyahu-for-humanitarian-pauses-discusses-plans-for-a-post-hamas-gaza/0000018b-ae50-df42-a78f-af53709f0000</guid></item><item><title>七国集团在东京举行密集会议后就以色列与哈马斯战争表现出统一立场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/g7-nations-show-unified-stance-on-israel-hamas-war-after-intensive-meetings-in-tokyo/0000018b-ae06-d0f8-a39b-fe1e1e620000</link><description>七国集团对哈马斯袭击以色列的批评与推动采取“紧急行动”帮助加沙平民寻求食物、水、医疗和住所保持平衡</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 09:46:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/g7-nations-show-unified-stance-on-israel-hamas-war-after-intensive-meetings-in-tokyo/0000018b-ae06-d0f8-a39b-fe1e1e620000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方告诉高等法院，反对以色列国防军加沙行动的示威活动可能会扰乱公共秩序</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/police-tell-high-court-that-demonstrations-against-idf-gaza-op-may-disrupt-public-order/0000018b-adf5-d5aa-a19f-affffad90000</link><description>以色列警方禁止了阿拉伯城镇的两场抗议活动，理由是早些时候的集会中听到了支持恐怖主义的口号。反对该禁令的请愿者表示，该禁令“是对抗议自由、政治表达自由和平等权的嘲弄”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 08:42:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/police-tell-high-court-that-demonstrations-against-idf-gaza-op-may-disrupt-public-order/0000018b-adf5-d5aa-a19f-affffad90000</guid></item><item><title>西方外交官警告说，在加沙地带重建犹太人定居点的言论损害了以色列的合法性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/western-diplomats-warn-talk-of-returning-settlements-in-gaza-damages-israeli-legitimacy/0000018b-abaa-da30-a38b-ffaf56170000</link><description>一名以色列高级官员承认，“显然，如果这件事从言辞变成行动，我们将遭受重大损失，但目前情况仍在控制之中。”一位欧洲大使表示，公众的支持活动正在受到监控，令人担忧</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 07:25:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/western-diplomats-warn-talk-of-returning-settlements-in-gaza-damages-israeli-legitimacy/0000018b-abaa-da30-a38b-ffaf56170000</guid></item><item><title>随着哈马斯的挖掘，以色列现在看到了加沙隧道的真实范围和复杂性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/as-hamas-digs-in-israel-sees-the-true-scope-and-sophistication-of-the-gaza-tunnels/0000018b-aba3-d5aa-a19f-affb2f3f0000</link><description>加沙地带的战斗比内塔尼亚胡试图描绘的“惊人的成功”要复杂一些。以色列国防军逐渐了解到，所有以色列情报部门都知道哈马斯在加沙下挖掘的一系列防御隧道，但这并没有触及该项目的表面。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 04:12:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/as-hamas-digs-in-israel-sees-the-true-scope-and-sophistication-of-the-gaza-tunnels/0000018b-aba3-d5aa-a19f-affb2f3f0000</guid></item><item><title>特莱布因以色列与哈马斯的言论和捍卫“河流到海洋”的口号而受到谴责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/tlaib-censured-for-israel-hamas-rhetoric-defense-of-river-to-the-sea-slogan/0000018b-acfc-da30-a38b-fffd7a960000</link><description>众议员拉什达·特莱布（Rashida Tlaib）是国会中唯一的巴勒斯坦裔美国人，被指控呼吁“摧毁以色列国和对犹太人进行种族灭绝”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Nov 2023 03:46:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-08/ty-article/.premium/tlaib-censured-for-israel-hamas-rhetoric-defense-of-river-to-the-sea-slogan/0000018b-acfc-da30-a38b-fffd7a960000</guid></item></channel></rss>